column5: Hidden in the Texas Hill Country.. Lake front property with Dock Access.. down the street from Willie's house, Recording Studio, Golf Course, Restaurants on the water, family-friendly activities, nightlife, Legendary Honky-Tonk Poodies Hill Top Bar & Grill, 30 mins from Downtown Austin. Your Lake Life starts here. Quite time, Great Fishing, Wakeboarding, Swimming,  RELAX! - you deserve it.
column8: Lakeside Lake House, on the Water, Private Dock
